        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>meat-free mince</strong> <strong>mixture</strong> and roll into 3 small sausage shapes per person – these are your <strong>Cypriot-style meat-free mince kebabs</strong></p><p>Lightly oil a baking tray (or two!) with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and add the <strong>Cypriot-style meat-free mince kebabs</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 12-15 min or until the kebabs are cooked through and browned</p>",
