    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the kebabs are cooking, cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways, then slice roughly on a diagonal</p><p>Dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Roughly tear the <strong>remaining parsley</strong></p>",
