      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Cypriot-style meat-free mince kebabs</strong> with the <strong>sumac salad</strong> and<strong> warmed chilli pitta</strong> to the side</p><p>Sprinkle over the<strong> remaining</strong> <strong>ground sumac </strong>and garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
